again will highlight improvements
to your design system or

36
00:02:13.933 --> 00:02:19.019
something gets revealed in in some
usability testing or something like that.

37
00:02:19.019 --> 00:02:21.479
And you will need to do a second or

38
00:02:21.479 --> 00:02:25.501
third version of a design
component to get it right.

