the logo, and maybe changing some styling,

43
00:02:42.884 --> 00:02:44.972
like drop shadows and rounded corners.

44
00:02:44.972 --> 00:02:46.891
Well, we've set all of those things.

45
00:02:46.891 --> 00:02:49.721
Your logo will be a component, right?

46
00:02:49.721 --> 00:02:52.142
So that means you can just go in and
replace it, and

47
00:02:52.142 --> 00:02:54.689
it'll ripple through the whole lot,
everywhere.

48
00:02:54.689 --> 00:02:58.386
The colors are set as variables, so
you can replace it in the variables and

49
00:02:58.386 --> 00:03:00.238
it'll ripple through everywhere.

50
00:03:00.238 --> 00:03:05.001
And the rounded corners and the shadows
are all set as styles, so again,

51
00:03:05.001 --> 00:03:07.433
it'll ripple through everywhere.

52
00:03:07.433 --> 00:03:12.129
So actually rebranding an entire site
becomes quite straightforward if it's

